off the table now.

17:16.122 --> 17:19.168
But for the first time ever,
we have a fully functioning plan

17:19.212 --> 17:20.604
to save the world.

17:20.648 --> 17:22.954
Let's not blow it up
before we get the chance.

17:22.998 --> 17:26.784
We've got greater aspirations
when we take down the asteroid.

17:26.828 --> 17:29.613
Look, if we truly want
to change the world,

17:29.657 --> 17:30.962
we need leverage.

17:31.006 --> 17:35.402
There is no plan
to give them up, is there?

17:35.445 --> 17:38.187
We're the new superpower.

17:38.231 --> 17:41.451
Everything that we've been
fighting for-- free speech,

17:41.495 --> 17:44.193
freedom of information,
power to the people--

17:44.237 --> 17:47.066
we can finally make it so.

17:47.109 --> 17:48.110
And in the meantime,
you're just gonna

17:48.154 --> 17:49.459
drop a bomb on New York City.

17:49.503 --> 17:50.765
You're not gonna lose
an ounce of sleep.

17:50.808 --> 17:52.549
Darius started that.And you're gonna finish it.

17:52.593 --> 17:54.116
And you're gonna kill
millions of people.

17:54.160 --> 17:57.815
After this project's done, so
are we. RE/SYST can go to hell.

17:57.859 --> 17:59.861
Liam.

17:59.904 --> 18:02.429
Hey.

18:06.607 --> 18:08.261
And as the standoff continues

18:08.304 --> 18:09.523
between RE/SYST
and President Tanz,

18:09.566 --> 18:12.439
the president has been
strangely silent.

18:12.482 --> 18:14.136
With the rail gun test
scheduled to go off

18:14.180 --> 18:15.964
just 12 hours from now,

18:16.007 --> 18:19.402
New Yorkers are fleeing
the city in droves.

18:25.495 --> 18:27.541
Hi.
Nate.

18:27.584 --> 18:29.282
What are you doing here?

18:29.325 --> 18:30.544
You seemed so down today,

18:30.587 --> 18:32.372
I thought maybe
I could cheer you up.

18:32.415 --> 18:33.634
And I came bearing gifts.

18:33.677 --> 18:37.594
Remember Bass Shepherd?

18:37.638 --> 18:39.640
Hello, Jillian.
Can we come in?

18:40.684 --> 18:41.946
Uh...

18:41.990 --> 18:44.166
Sure. Come.

18:49.215 --> 18:51.521
:
What?

18:59.225 --> 19:01.488
