Tech Con One, we've entered
the warehouse.

19:27.340 --> 19:29.385
MAN 2:
Bravo Team, hold for Alpha.

19:31.431 --> 19:34.608
Bravo Team, we're on
the passenger. Weapons free.

19:34.651 --> 19:38.002
MAN:
Copy that, Alpha. Good hunting.

19:38.046 --> 19:40.048
Freeze! Nobody move!

19:40.091 --> 19:42.790
Gun down, gun down!

19:42.833 --> 19:45.836
Whoa, whoa, whoa, don't shoot,
don't shoot, don't shoot.

19:45.880 --> 19:49.100
MAN:
Area's secure, Mr. Secretary.

19:49.144 --> 19:50.624
She's over here.

19:50.667 --> 19:51.799
Clear.

