with your captors.You're the idiot.

32:45.006 --> 32:46.965
This is not the time
to undermine RE/SYST.

32:47.008 --> 32:49.054
We have Aguirre; he is
gonna save the world.

32:49.097 --> 32:51.012
Aguirre is Darius.

32:51.056 --> 32:53.928
What?

32:53.972 --> 32:57.105
MAN: All personnel, firing test
begins in eight minutes.

32:57.149 --> 32:58.977
