33:05.722 --> 33:08.421
MAN: Security measures
have been initiated.

33:08.464 --> 33:10.423
All computer systems are now
in lockdown mode.

33:10.466 --> 33:12.033
What's going on?

33:12.077 --> 33:14.383
Darius changed the codes.

33:14.427 --> 33:16.255
I'm locked out.

33:16.298 --> 33:18.474
He's the only one
that can stop the test.

33:18.518 --> 33:20.694
There's nothing I can do.

33:20.737 --> 33:23.175
