in seven minutes, Grace,

33:23.218 --> 33:25.090
whether we like it or not.

33:31.879 --> 33:35.056
Thank you, General.
We've done all we can.

33:35.100 --> 33:37.885
They've been evacuating
the entire tristate area

33:37.928 --> 33:39.887
for the last 24 hours
to prevent loss of life.

33:39.930 --> 33:41.454
Harris, none of this
makes sense.

33:41.497 --> 33:44.674
And the way Darius disappeared.

33:44.718 --> 33:46.676
I know it's crazy,
but is it possible

33:46.720 --> 33:49.766
this is all some elaborate
"Darius" plan?

33:49.810 --> 33:53.422
If it is, it better work, fast.

33:55.076 --> 33:55.990
NEWSWOMAN:
As the rail gun test

33:56.034 --> 33:58.601
is set to launch imminently,

33:58.645 --> 34:01.126
RE/SYST's nuclear threat
hangs over our head.

34:01.169 --> 34:03.867
And still no sign
of our president.

34:03.911 --> 34:06.044
All right, I need
to address the group.

34:07.132 --> 34:08.785
Where's Liam?

34:08.829 --> 34:13.094
Is it true that Aguirre
is Darius Tanz?

34:13.138 --> 34:15.053
W-We deserve answers.

34:15.096 --> 34:18.012
Yes.

34:18.056 --> 34:21.842
I guess Liam beat me
to the punch with the news.

34:21.885 --> 34:23.974
But Darius
will cooperate fully

34:24.018 --> 34:26.020
and he will continue to help us
with our project,

34:26.064 --> 34:27.413
so there's no reason
to be concerned.

34:27.456 --> 34:29.067
Really?

34:29.110 --> 34:30.503
Well, that's-that's
